You sit behind the wheel on the west coast in San Francisco and your mission is to arrive first in New York.
The idea has interesting elements.
The itinerary is divided into ten steps and then into more than 50 races.
As a result, each race takes place on another route and the steps planned in different environments that are quite different and interesting.
The player does not have the feeling for a single moment that the game offers him something unique.
Some environments are quite beautiful, although the graphic technical level is of the same type as the previous series.
