For its Costa Rican followers, the fact that Pearl Jam will happen in Costa Rica is a dream come true. Are you aware of what your fans live?
Going to Costa Rica is a dream that has come true for us too.
This is our second time in South and Central America, and so far this has been great.
I only spent my vacation in Costa Rica once; it's such a beautiful country and I think we can spend a few days there.
